#

Creamy Akkaravadisal

$15.99
400 kcal

Allergens:

Nuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

DessertIndian CuisineFestiveSweet

Description

A rich and creamy rice pudding made with aromatic spices, perfect for any festive occasion!

Ingredients

  • Rice: 1 cup
  • Moong Dal: 1/4 cup
  • Jaggery: 3/4 cup
  • Coconut Milk: 1 cup
  • Cardamom Powder: 1 tsp
  • Ghee: 2 tbsp
  • Cashews: 2 tbsp
  • Raisins: 2 tbsp
  • Water: 3 cups
